I really, heartfully recommend her to everyone who want to have peaceful pregnancy journey. Thanks doctor for all your support.

Dr. Dhivya is a highly skilled gynecologist who provided exceptional care throughout my pregnancy journey. From the very beginning, she was approachable, friendly, and put me at ease with her warm demeanor.

Dr. Dhivya is a great listener, and she took the time to understand my concerns and questions. She provided clear explanations and made sure that I fully understood my options at every step of the process. She also encouraged me to ask questions and never made me feel rushed or pressured.

Overall, I highly recommend Dr. Dhivya for anyone looking for a caring and approachable gynecologist who is highly skilled in maternity and delivery care.
